Adeola Deborah Olubamiji bụ onye Naijiria-Canada na-ahụ maka teknụzụ bụ ọkachamara na mmepụta ihe mgbakwunye ígwè na plastik (nke a makwaara dị ka mbipụta 3D). N'afọ 2017, ọ ghọrọ onye isi ojii mbụ nwetara nchizu akwụkwọPhD na Injinia Biomedical site na Mahadum Saskatchewan dị afọ 112, Canada. Ọ gara n'ihu na-ekwu okwu TEDx banyere otu o si eji mbipụta 3D maka mgbake nke cartilage nkwonkwo mebiri emebi na Canada.
